        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2577",
        "content": "No one would believe it; and if they did, and wrote to thank mother, she would think-well, goodness only knew what she would think.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
